{"tid":1121001,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【等待囡囡來臨】52歲陳麗麗陀B精神飽滿 黃澤鋒：期待初夏","createTime":"2019-04-23T05:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T23:49:35.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8300902f0003bac6971a29ad6abb90ad600e83eb","tid":1121001,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T05:10:26.000Z","msg":"黃澤鋒年初宣佈52歲老婆陳麗麗懷孕，陳麗麗早前被妊娠濕疹折騰周身痕，幸好有老公黃澤鋒悉心照顧，現在已痊癒，日前出席活動，黃澤鋒稱太太預產期在7月。<br />\n昨晚他在IG貼出老婆大肚相，二人笑得合不攏嘴，留言：「期待初夏，妳的來臨！」雖然太太是高齡孕婦，不過她亦精神飽滿，向網民分享他們內心的喜悅。<br />\n目前黃澤鋒都小心照顧懷孕愛妻的日常起居飲食，下個月已安排拍攝懷孕照留念，囡囡乳名叫「小黃妃」，中文名交由師傅改，因為太太不希望老公為子女改壞名，坦言有意再追B。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190423/large/1555987872_4b47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190423%2Flarge%2F1555987872_4b47.jpg&h=0eb7264e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190423/59518642\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190423%2F59518642&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OK3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=39ee456c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190423%2F59518642&h=86a2a7f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190423/59518642</a>"},{"pid":"759023e9126a478b12cbb43a3eeef844848e02ff","tid":1121001,"uid":227275,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T05:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ddcd87b6516cb78a2f2f168ee970d23e3f04d4e","tid":1121001,"uid":249562,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T05:16:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a